'''Sumber pambalajaran tabukak''', atau disingkek dalam bahaso Inggirih, '''OER''' (''open educational resources''), adolah [[dokumen]] jo [[media]] [[Isi tabukak|balisensi tabukak]] nan baguno untuak tujuan [[pangajaran]], [[pambalajaran]], [[pandidikan]], panilaian, jo [[panalitian]]. OER antaro lain malingkupi kuliah, bahan kuliah, modul konten, objek pambalajaran, jurnal, sarato babagai paralatan pandukuang panyampaian konten pambalajaran tasabuik. Istilah open education resources dipakai jo [[UNESCO]] patamo kali pado taun 2002 dalam ({{baso-en|Forum on the Impact of Open Courseware for Higher Education in Developing Countries}}).<ref name="Johnstone">{{Cite journal | volume = 28 | issue = 3 | last = Johnstone | first = Sally M. | title = Open Educational Resources Serve the World | journal = Educause Quarterly | accessdate = 2010-11-01 | year = 2005 | url = http://www.educause.edu/EDUCAUSE+Quarterly/EDUCAUSEQuarterlyMagazineVolum/OpenEducationalResourcesServet/157357 }}</ref> Pamarintah [[Indonesia]] manyatokan dukuangannyo pado sumber pambalajaran tabukak ko pado pasal 79 ayat 4 Undang-Undang Nomor 12 Taun 2012 Tantang Pandidikan Tinggi.<ref>[http://www.depdagri.go.id/media/documents/2012/08/27/u/u/uu_no.12-2012.pdf Undang-Undang Republik Indonesia Nomor 12 Taun 2012 Tentang Pendidikan Tinggi]</ref>

